        <div class="col-xs-12">
            <h1 class="cd-text cd-title">sash</h1>
            <p class="cd-text">A good use of sashes is to call out extra information such as a discounted price, or a preferred choice. These sashes are intended for use with <a href="panels">panels</a> or <a href="features">feature blocks</a>.</p>

            <h2 class="cd-text cd-title">position</h2>
            <p class="cd-text">A left or right modifier is a requirement for a working sash.</p>
            <h3 class="cd-text cd-title">sash left</h3>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3">
