            <h2 class="cd-text cd-title">colour</h2>
            <p class="cd-text">The default sash is typically used to communicate promotional information e.g. a discount. The highlight variant is typically used to highlight a new or promoted item.</p>
            <h3 class="cd-text cd-title">sash highlight</h3>
            <div class="row">
